params._account: The address of the end user account making the deposit
params._wantAmt: The amount of Want token to deposit (must already be transferred)

params._amountUSDC: The amount of USDC to exchange for Want token (must already be deposited on this contract)

returns._0: uint256 Amount of Want token obtained

params._amount: The Want token quantity to exchange
params._maxMarketMovementAllowed: The max slippage allowed for swaps. 1000 = 0 %, 995 = 0.5%, etc.

returns._0: uint256 Amount of USDC token obtained

params._amount: The amount of the tokens to transfer
params._to: The address to transfer tokens to
params._token: Address of the ERC20 token to transfer

params._initValue: A VaultStandardAMMInit struct with all constructor params
params._timelockOwner: The designated timelock controller address to act as owner

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

paused().details: Returns true if the contract is paused, and false otherwise.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions anymore. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby removing any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._entranceFeeFactor: Entrance fee numerator (higher means smaller percentage)
params._withdrawFeeFactor: Withdrawal fee numerator (higher means smaller percentage)

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

params._wantAmt: The amount of Want token to withdraw
